<P><H1 align=center>EXISTING / PREVIOUS MORTGAGES – DC070</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red><STRONG>NOTE: </STRONG>areas shown in red are mandatory and must be completed to 
proceed</FONT>           </P>
<P>This screen shows a summary of any mortgage accounts held previously, 
including existing mortgages. The information collected may be used to assess 
the applicant’s suitability and the affordability of the new mortgage. If the 
applicant has a current mortgage or has had one in the last three years, click 
on the ‘Yes’ radio button, which will enable the ‘Add’ button</P>
<P><H3>Add: </H3>clicking on ‘Add’ leads to <A HREF="HELP_DC071.asp">Add / Edit 
Mortgage Account (DC071)</A> 
<P></P>
<P><H3>Edit: </H3>to edit details entered, highlight the 
record and click on ‘Edit’ 
<P></P>
<P><H3>Delete: </H3>to delete a record, highlight it and click 
on ‘Delete’
<P></P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>clicking on OK leads to the next screen.
<P></P>
